The App implements 3 web services
/features
/features/{id}
/features/{id}/quicklook

These web services follow the rules of Richardson Maturity Model and hence follow the best practices. 

Instructions to package the App. 

1. From the top level directory of the project execute
mvn clean package

2. Step 1 should generate a jar file in the target directory. To run this jar file execute: 
java -jar UP42-CC-0.0.1.jar

3. When the server is started, open a browser and write the following URL in the address bar: 
 http://localhost:8080/features
 
